Naspers Targeting Latin America, Eastern Europe, Southeast Asia, CEO Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-10-13T05:11:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/naspers-targeting-latin-america-eastern-europe-to-expand-ceo-bekker-says.html
Naspers Ltd. (NPN) ,  South Africa ’s largest
media group, is targeting opportunities in  Latin America ,
 Southeast Asia  and Eastern Europe, according to Chief Executive
Officer Koos Bekker.  The company, based in  Cape Town , has “looked at”
Argentina and  Mexico , Bekker said in an interview published by
technology website Memeburn.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  